After the juggernaut that was The Penguin, we continue our tour through the dark alleys of Gotham, just in time to review the latest animated project about everyone's favorite cowled detective, Batman: The Caped Crusader! Join us as we compare it to its predecessor Batman: The Animated series, discuss this era of Batman lore, and debate whether the changes that were made have hurt or helped this series shine. It's a must-listen for Batman fans, so grab your gadgets, pick up your cowl and join us for this detailed breakdown of Batman: Caped Crusader! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

